**Item #:** SCP-XXXX

**Object Class:** Safe

**Special Containment Procedures:** Like, why are we wasting our time trying to contain these entities!? Just pour lava on the mother fucker and call it a day! (also he likes to watch movies with Tom Cruise in them for some reason so make him watch the goddamn movies for 24 hours straight!) 

**Description:** The SCP is just some random British dude that likes cheddar. Idk why he likes cheddar so don't ask me. Yeh. Idk he is not dangerous, he just some random British guy we snagged behind a subway. I mean, I think he has some sort of anomaly or something wrong with him, but as far as I know he is just a random British guy.
